description: Calculate when a team becomes ownerless or a bot team. Just by filling in the date of last login. Please note that a team only become ownerless when the owner didn't log-in on the second exactly 49 days. Therefore it could seem to take 50 days. A second team will turn to ownerless in 7 days from supporter package expiration instead of 49 days. This tool owned to GM-Noortje and HagOnline.
